anity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/929c1763478c6ed3215b0f522602d37f.poster.avif?t=1748553992\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/929c1763478c6ed3215b0f522602d37f.webm?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/929c1763478c6ed3215b0f522602d37f.mp4?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>RELIVE THE GOLDEN AGE OF RETRO VIDEO GAMES</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With graphics and a soundtrack that evoke the golden age of retro video games, OYASUMII will immerse you in a world of nostalgia and excitement. Prepare for a unique adventure that will take you to the limits of your fears and challenge you to explore the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/fd1abf000bd4cd514f79603a2f02f74c.poster.avif?t=1748553992\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/fd1abf000bd4cd514f79603a2f02f74c.webm?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/fd1abf000bd4cd514f79603a2f02f74c.mp4?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>GET READY FOR AN UNFORGETTABLE ADVENTURE</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to discover the hidden secrets of OYAS